      <title>印尼债券计划激发了对治理，货币化的恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/indonesian-bond-plan-sparks-fears-over-governance-monetization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚银行购买将由政府发行的债券资助其雄心勃勃的住房计划的计划，这引起了人们对该国债务治理的更多关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/indonesian-bond-plan-sparks-fears-over-governance-monetization</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 01:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金的速度持续希望，避风港的需求不断增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-amid-growing-us-rate-cut-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着信心的增长，美联储将在7月份实施另一种削减税率，而特朗普政府针对中国的最新贸易萨尔沃（Salvos）则支持避风港的需求，这是最新记录的最新记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-amid-growing-us-rate-cut-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 00:28:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴菲特的赌注Sparks在日本贸易房屋的股票激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/japan-s-trading-houses-surge-as-buffett-looks-to-boost-stakes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司（Berkshire Hathaway Inc.）增加持股的计划后，包括三菱公司和马鲁贝尼公司（Marubeni Corp.）在内的日本贸易公司周二集会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/japan-s-trading-houses-surge-as-buffett-looks-to-boost-stakes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 00:14:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港解决赤字，预算的经济增长降低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/hong-kong-to-tackle-deficit-slower-economic-growth-in-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港官员本周将发布有关如何解决亚洲金融资本面临的越来越挑战的计划。他们的主要成长速度较慢，是二十年来最长的财政缺陷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/hong-kong-to-tackle-deficit-slower-economic-growth-in-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油随着美国对伊朗震撼原油市场的新制裁而上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在特朗普政府对伊朗石油流动实施新的制裁后的第二天，石油升起了第二天，这将这一举动构筑为恢复对德黑兰的最大压力策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 23:22:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港，亚洲股票随着美国的压力下降：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统遏制中国投资的举动并征收加拿大和墨西哥的关税促使投资者降低风险赌注后，亚洲股票下跌。交易结束时，美国股票的下降也损害了情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 22:35:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大的TFI Abandons在股东反弹之后移交给我们</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/tfi-to-remain-in-canada-after-investor-critiqued-move-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大卡车运输公司TFI International Inc.推翻了将其法律总部转移到美国的决定，称股东表示反对这一想法后，它正在下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/tfi-to-remain-in-canada-after-investor-critiqued-move-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 21:55:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币的“糟糕情绪”继续对Altcoins，Ether称重</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/crypto-s-poor-sentiment-continues-to-weigh-on-altcoins-ether</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ether和许多更高的Altcoins（例如Solana和Dogecoin）仍处于压力下，而投资者上周在其有史以来最大的黑客攻击之后，该行业仍在卷起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/crypto-s-poor-sentiment-continues-to-weigh-on-altcoins-ether</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 18:55:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国阿德尔人对特朗普的命令跌跌撞撞，以阿里巴巴的10％暴跌领导</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/alibaba-shares-tumble-as-trump-order-stirs-china-trade-angst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2022年以来，在唐纳德·特朗普总统的最新指示引起了人们对加深世界上两个最大经济体之间的财务和技术脱钩的担忧之后，中国股票在周一在美国交易中跌落，这是在阿里巴巴集团持有有限公司的最大抛售带领下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/alibaba-shares-tumble-as-trump-order-stirs-china-trade-angst</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 16:24:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
